          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Bureau Research Transparency Act </b></p> <p> Amends the Consumer Financial Protection Act of 2010 to require the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau, any time it issues a research paper available to the public, to accompany it with all studies, data, and other analyses on which it was based.</p>]]></text>
